<template>
  <v-container>
    <v-row justify="center">
      <v-col cols="12" md="8">
        <v-card>
          <v-row>
            <v-col cols="12" md="4">
              <v-img :src="agent.profilePic" height="300"></v-img>
            </v-col>
            <v-col cols="12" md="8">
              <v-card-title>{{ agent.name }}</v-card-title>
              <v-card-subtitle>{{ agent.title }}</v-card-subtitle>
              <v-card-text>
                <v-list>
                  <v-list-item v-for="(contact, index) in agent.contacts" :key="index">
                    <v-list-item-icon>
                      <v-icon>{{ contact.icon }}</v-icon>
                    </v-list-item-icon>
                    <v-list-item-content>
                      <v-list-item-title>{{ contact.value }}</v-list-item-title>
                    </v-list-item-content>
                  </v-list-item>
                </v-list>
              </v-card-text>
            </v-col>
          </v-row>
        </v-card>
      </v-col>
    </v-row>
  </v-container>
</template>

<script>
export default {
  name: 'Agent',
  data: () => ({
    agent: {
      name: 'Adrian Tan',
      title: 'Executive Director',
      profilePic: '/src/assets/background.jpg',
      contacts: [
        { icon: 'mdi-phone', value: '+65 12345678' },
        { icon: 'mdi-whatsapp', value: 'WhatsApp link here' },
        { icon: 'mdi-instagram', value: '@instagram name n link' },
        { icon: 'mdi-telegram', value: '@telegram' }
      ]
    }
  })
}
</script>
